1265
01:46:40.686 --> 01:46:43.898
Chef, pick up that weapon!
Pick it up! Pick it up!

1266
01:46:43.981 --> 01:46:45.742
Stand fast! Captain—

1267
01:46:45.766 --> 01:46:47.066
