1282
01:48:21.921 --> 01:48:24.673
And it will be such until we are all dead.

1283
01:48:30.747 --> 01:48:32.147
<i>To my command!</i>

1284
01:48:32.872 --> 01:48:33.772
Attention!

1285
01:48:34.396 --> 01:48:35.296
Shoulder!

1286
01:48:58.097 --> 01:49:00.097
Present arms!

1287
01:49:06.321 --> 01:49:07.421
