01:51:38.142 --> 01:51:40.142
You still need to study with Mr. Robert.

1296
01:51:40.666 --> 01:51:41.466
Let’s go.

1297
01:51:41.490 --> 01:51:43.490
Not too bad.
Everyone to bed, now.

