He's of a Paratroop Regiment.

1312
01:52:48.687 --> 01:52:50.856
- Madame Sarrault.
- Captain.

1313
01:53:05.180 --> 01:53:06.480
<i>“An angel passes...”</i>

1314
01:53:06.504 --> 01:53:07.704
<i>“…Let’s butcher it!”</i>

1315
01:53:11.328 --> 01:53:12.927
